nodes.name: oxalate:CoA ligase (AMP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + Oxalate + CoA <=> AMP + Diphosphate + Oxalyl-CoA

nodes.name: glycolaldehyde:NAD+ oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: Glycolaldehyde + NAD+ + H2O <=> Glycolate + NADH + H+

nodes.name: 1,2-Ethanediol:NAD+ oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: Ethylene glycol + NAD+ <=> Glycolaldehyde + NADH + H+

nodes.name: glycine:NAD+ 2-oxidoreductase (tetrahydrofolate-methylene-adding)
nodes.rxn: Glycine + Tetrahydrofolate + NAD+ <=> 5,10-Methylenetetrahydrofolate + Ammonia + CO2 + NADH + H+

nodes.name: L-glutamate:ferredoxin oxidoreductase (transaminating)
nodes.rxn: 2 L-Glutamate + 2 Oxidized ferredoxin <=> L-Glutamine + 2-Oxoglutarate + 2 Reduced ferredoxin + 2 H+

nodes.name: L-Glutamate:ammonia ligase (ADP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + L-Glutamate + Ammonia <=> ADP + Orthophosphate + L-Glutamine

nodes.name: Acetate:CoA ligase (AMP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + Acetate + CoA <=> AMP + Diphosphate + Acetyl-CoA
